    {"children":[{"type":"text","value":"平安 is deeply valued in Chinese culture as the ideal state of existence. It represents not just\nphysical safety but also spiritual peace and family harmony. Wishing someone 平安 is one of the most\nheartfelt blessings in Chinese culture, encompassing protection from harm and inner tranquility."}],"type":"paragraph"}
